P0 SET UP


1) Start a new project

2) Add the app

3) Adapt/mix the setting up
- Time zone langage
- Database
- Installed App
- Logging/mail if needed

4) Add the UTF 8 everywhere

# -*- coding:utf-8 -*-

4bis) Add Media/static directories if needed

5) Syncdb + del Migrations

5) Bis add your models to the admin 

6) Comment Index in urls.py

7) Launch admin!








